get.description:
Server-Sent Events stream for real-time updates.

SECURITY (Phase 18.0):
- Authentication required when SSE_AUTH_REQUIRED=true
- Validates user can access requested correlation_id
- Filters events to only those user is authorized to see

Features:
- Filter by correlation_id to only receive relevant events
- Reconnection support via Last-Event-ID header or query param
- Automatic replay of missed events
- 30-second heartbeat to keep connection alive

Example:
    const eventSource = new EventSource('/api/events/stream?correlation_id=deal-123');
    eventSource.onmessage = (event) => {
        const data = JSON.parse(event.data);
        console.log(data.type, data.data);
    };
